thread.title: BRIEF-CPH Chemie Und Papier Holding FY EBIT Down At CHF 2.9 Mln

author: Reuters Editorial
title: BRIEF-CPH Chemie Und Papier Holding FY EBIT Down At CHF 2.9 Mln

organizations.name: cph chemie und papier holding ag

text:
Feb 20 (Reuters) - CPH Chemie Und Papier Holding AG:
* FY SALES INCREASE OF 8.0% TO CHF 469.8 MILLION * FY NET RESULT FOR THE YEAR WAS IMPROVED BY CHF 23.9 MILLION TO CHF 16.2 MILLION
* DIVIDEND PAYMENT FOR THE YEAR REMAINS UNCHANGED AT CHF 0.65 PER SHARE
* OUTLOOK 2018: TO REPORT HIGHER SALES AND A CLEARLY IMPROVED OPERATING RESULT
* FY EBIT 2.9 MILLION CHF VERSUS 5.9 MILLION CHF YEAR AGO Further company coverage: (Gdynia Newsroom)
